NETWORK USE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Orbit Axis is offered to users over a network. Section 13 of the AGPL means that
anyone who interacts with it remotely is entitled to receive its complete
corresponding source code.

The application satisfies this in two ways:

  - GET /api/v1/source  — a machine-readable statement of licence, versions,
                          and where the source can be obtained
  - /source             — the same information as a page a person can read

